CaseTeamMemberProgram.name: CaseTeamMemberProgram
CaseTeamMemberProgram.description: Represents mapping information between Case Team Member and Program.

CaseId.description: The case that's associated with the case team member.

CaseTeamMember.description: The case team member that is mapped to one or more programs.

CurrencyIsoCode.description: The ISO code for the currency.

LastReferencedDate.description: The timestamp when the current user last accessed this record, a record related to this record, or a list view.

LastViewedDate.description: The timestamp when the current user last viewed this record or list view. If this value is null, the user might have only accessed this record or list view (LastReferencedDate) but not viewed it.

Name.description: The name of the case team member program record.

ProgramId.description: The program that is mapped to case team members.
